{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "古者明王聖人所以王天下、正諸侯者，彼其愛民謹忠，利民謹厚，忠信相連，又示之以利，是以終身不饜，歿世而不卷，古者明王聖人，其所以王天下、正諸侯者，此也。", "text_normalized": "古者明王聖人所以王天下、正諸侯者，彼其愛民謹忠，利民謹厚，忠信相連，又示之以利，是以終身不饜，歿世而不卷，古者明王聖人，其所以王天下、正諸侯者，此也。", "canonical_ref": "20.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "是故古者聖王制為節用之法，曰：", "text_normalized": "是故古者聖王制為節用之法，曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "凡天下群百工，輪、車、鞼、匏、陶、冶、梓匠，使各從事其所能。", "text_normalized": "凡天下群百工，輪、車、鞼、匏、陶、冶、梓匠，使各從事其所能。", "canonical_ref": "20.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "凡足以奉給民用，則止。", "text_normalized": "凡足以奉給民用，則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "諸加費不加於民利者，聖王弗為。", "text_normalized": "諸加費不加於民利者，聖王弗為。", "canonical_ref": "20.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "古者聖王制為飲食之法，曰：", "text_normalized": "古者聖王制為飲食之法，曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "足以充虛繼氣，強股肱，耳目聰明，則止。", "text_normalized": "足以充虛繼氣，強股肱，耳目聰明，則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "不極五味之調、芬香之和，不致遠國珍怪異物。", "text_normalized": "不極五味之調、芬香之和，不致遠國珍怪異物。", "canonical_ref": "20.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "何以知其然？", "text_normalized": "何以知其然？", "canonical_ref": "20.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "古者堯治天下，南撫交阯，北降幽都，東西至日所出入，莫不賓服。", "text_normalized": "古者堯治天下，南撫交阯，北降幽都，東西至日所出入，莫不賓服。", "canonical_ref": "20.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "逮至其厚愛，黍稷不二，羹胾不重，飯於土塯，啜於土形，斗以酌。", "text_normalized": "逮至其厚愛，黍稷不二，羹胾不重，飯於土塯，啜於土形，斗以酌。", "canonical_ref": "20.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "俯仰周旋威儀之禮，聖王弗為。", "text_normalized": "俯仰周旋威儀之禮，聖王弗為。", "canonical_ref": "20.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "古者聖王制為衣服之法，曰：", "text_normalized": "古者聖王制為衣服之法，曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "冬服紺緅之衣，輕且暖，夏服絺綌之衣，輕且清，則止。", "text_normalized": "冬服紺緅之衣，輕且暖，夏服絺綌之衣，輕且清，則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "諸加費不加於民利者，聖王弗為。", "text_normalized": "諸加費不加於民利者，聖王弗為。", "canonical_ref": "20.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "古者聖人為猛禽狡獸暴人害民，於是教民以兵行。", "text_normalized": "古者聖人為猛禽狡獸暴人害民，於是教民以兵行。", "canonical_ref": "20.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "日帶劍，為刺則入，擊則斷，旁擊而不折，此劍之利也。", "text_normalized": "日帶劍，為刺則入，擊則斷，旁擊而不折，此劍之利也。", "canonical_ref": "20.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "甲為衣則輕且利，動則兵且從，此甲之利也。", "text_normalized": "甲為衣則輕且利，動則兵且從，此甲之利也。", "canonical_ref": "20.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "車為服重致遠，乘之則安，引之則利，安以不傷人，利以速至，此車之利也。", "text_normalized": "車為服重致遠，乘之則安，引之則利，安以不傷人，利以速至，此車之利也。", "canonical_ref": "20.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "古者聖王為大川廣谷之不可濟，於是利為舟楫，足以將之則止。", "text_normalized": "古者聖王為大川廣谷之不可濟，於是利為舟楫，足以將之則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "雖上者三公諸侯至，舟楫不易，津人不飾，此舟之利也。", "text_normalized": "雖上者三公諸侯至，舟楫不易，津人不飾，此舟之利也。", "canonical_ref": "20.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "古者聖王制為節葬之法，曰：", "text_normalized": "古者聖王制為節葬之法，曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "衣三領，足以朽肉，棺三寸，足以朽骸，堀穴深不通於泉，流不發洩，則止。", "text_normalized": "衣三領，足以朽肉，棺三寸，足以朽骸，堀穴深不通於泉，流不發洩，則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "死者既葬，生者毋久喪用哀。", "text_normalized": "死者既葬，生者毋久喪用哀。", "canonical_ref": "20.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "古者人之始生未有宮室之時，因陵丘堀穴而處焉。", "text_normalized": "古者人之始生未有宮室之時，因陵丘堀穴而處焉。", "canonical_ref": "20.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "聖王慮之，以為堀穴，曰：", "text_normalized": "聖王慮之，以為堀穴，曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "冬可以辟風寒。", "text_normalized": "冬可以辟風寒。", "canonical_ref": "20.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "逮夏，下潤濕，上熏烝，恐傷民之氣，於是作為宮室而利。", "text_normalized": "逮夏，下潤濕，上熏烝，恐傷民之氣，於是作為宮室而利。", "canonical_ref": "20.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "然則為宮室之法將奈何哉？", "text_normalized": "然則為宮室之法將奈何哉？", "canonical_ref": "20.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "20.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii", "source_id": "mozi-020-economy-of-expenditures-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "其旁可以圉風寒，上可以圉雪霜雨露，其中蠲潔，可以祭祀，宮牆足以為男女之別，則止。", "text_normalized": "其旁可以圉風寒，上可以圉雪霜雨露，其中蠲潔，可以祭祀，宮牆足以為男女之別，則止。", "canonical_ref": "20.33", "notes": ""}
